<reference id="class_leavechanneloptions">
    <title><ph keyref="LeaveChannelOptions"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc">离开频道的选择。</ph></shortdesc>
    <refbody>
        <section id="prototype">
            <p outputclass="codeblock">
            <codeblock props="android" outputclass="language-java"></codeblock>
            <codeblock props="ios mac" outputclass="language-objectivec"></codeblock>
            <codeblock props="windows" outputclass="language-cpp">struct LeaveChannelOptions {
  bool stopAudioMixing;
  bool stopAllEffect;
  bool stopMicrophoneRecording;
  LeaveChannelOptions() : stopAudioMixing(true), stopAllEffect(true), stopMicrophoneRecording(true) {}
};
</codeblock>
            <codeblock props="electron" outputclass="language-typescript"></codeblock>
            <codeblock props="unity" outputclass="language-csharp"></codeblock>
            <codeblock props="rn" outputclass="language-typescript"></codeblock>
            <codeblock props="flutter" outputclass="language-dart"></codeblock>
            </p>
        </section>
        <section id="parameters">
            <title><text conref="../../conref/conref_api_metadata.dita#metadata/property"/></title>
            <parml>
                <plentry>
                    <pt><?oxy-placeholder content="The name of the attribute or property."?>stopAudioMixing</pt>
                    <pd>离开频道时，是否停止播放音乐文件及混音：<ul id="ul_ttv_f2n_3qb">
                            <li><ph keyref="true"/>：（默认）停止。</li>
                            <li><ph keyref="false"/>： 不停止。</li>
                        </ul>
                    </pd>
                </plentry>
                <plentry>
                    <pt>stopAllEffect</pt>
                    <pd>离开频道时，是否停止播放音效：<ul id="ul_tgl_m2n_3qb">
                            <li><ph keyref="true"/>：（默认）停止。</li>
                            <li><ph keyref="false"/>： 不停止。</li>
                        </ul></pd>
                </plentry>
                <plentry>
                    <pt>stopMicrophoneRecording</pt>
                    <pd>离开频道时，是否停止麦克风采集：<ul id="ul_dy1_s2n_3qb">
                            <li><ph keyref="true"/>：（默认）停止。</li>
                            <li><ph keyref="false"/>： 不停止。</li>
                        </ul></pd>
                </plentry>
            </parml>
        </section>
